udAharaNe, $3$ peY idakekx rUpAya BinanxrAshigaLeSATxguvadu.
$3$ peY $1$ rUpAyige Aga takakxdudx $192$ peY.

\begin{center}
$\dfrac{3}{192}=\dfrac{1}{64}$ rUpAyi rUpavu.
\end{center}

idaralilx $3$ peYyanunx $1$ rUpAyige Aguva $192$ peYgaLiMda BAgisalu $\frac{3}{192}=\frac{1}{64}$ rUpAyigaLa rUpavu.\\

$2$ ANe $6$ kAsu idu rUpAyigaLa eSaTxneV BAgavu.\\

\begin{tabular}{ccc}
$2$\; ANe\;l $6$ kAsu & = $30$\; peY \\
$1$\; rUpAyi & =$192$\; peY 
\end{tabular}
\begin{tabular}{ccc}
$=\dfrac{10}{64}=\dfrac{5}{32}$\;  rUpAyigaLa BAgavu.
